Package: fars.functions
Title: Process, Summarize, and Map FARS Data 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given ="Building R Packages", role="aut")
    person(given = "Hannah", family = "Liyanarachchi", email = "hliyanar@yahoo.com", role = "cre")
Description: Reads in FARS (Fatality Analysis Reporting System) files containing FARS data. 
    It can also create a correctly formatted file name, create tibbles and summaries of the data across multiple years, and plot accident data by US state on a map. 
